{"tid":917567,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓子亮處男下海","createTime":"2018-11-26T13:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T13:54:45.000Z","uid":46587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d468917fae7e3809bf28a9d298c3501761638c5f","tid":917567,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://Now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNow.com&d=HAQPLkt2ds%2BdTv5hvldFIcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=9672ae00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Now.com</a>娛樂】歌手韓子亮（TL）上星期衝出香港，到泰國拍攝廣告。<br />\n<br />\n受泰國某酒店邀請的TL上星期飛到芭提雅，與整容逾30次、由大叔變鮮肉的當地男網紅金民豪分別為同一酒店拍攝宣傳片。一向「惜肉如金」行韓風的TL為了配合陽光與海灘的泰國，不惜「處男下海」，赤裸上身上陣！不過怕醜的他卻以獨角獸浮床「遮遮掩掩」，始終緊守「兩點」，最大尺度只是看到「肉背」。<br />\n<br />\n對於金民豪30次整容，TL說：「我覺得佢整容真係一個好成功嘅例子，都幾自然，雖然佢整咗30次可能係一件好辛苦嘅事，同埋冇人知道佢痛楚，但起碼佢呢一世係會賺得返。」雖然有見金民豪整容後即刻由醜八怪變成人生勝利組，不過TL就指不會考慮整容，他笑說：「我唔考慮喇，因為我個樣又冇佢未整之前咁差，咁我依家覺得正正常常，唔係好醜樣，又唔係好靚仔，夠做㗎喇！因為人比人、比死人，如果真係去整，整完啲人又可能覺得你唔整靚啲，唔整就最好喇。」TL又透露此行跟金民豪有傾談合作：「之後可能有機會大家一齊拍旅遊節目。」<br />\n<br />\n一首《Party with TL》唱到被90、00後奉為「歌神」的TL，去到泰國都不忘要繼續Party！收工後，TL「獨自去偷歡」到芭提雅內最大型的「荷里活酒吧」夜蒲，其間更有「艷遇」，有名泰國型男上前主動搭訕，TL最後亦有禮貌地應要求與對方頭貼頭合照。除了夜蒲外，TL還去了親親大自然，去野外嘗試了玩繩網，一展運動細胞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/entertainment/player?newsId=328496&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328496%26refer%3D&d=HAQPLkt2ds%2BdTv5hvldFIcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=ef2eec00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328496%26refer%3D&h=7585af66\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/entertainment/player?newsId=328496&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"5dbe05d951507ead33abaf4dc2774b8486b9a9df","tid":917567,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"tl真係香港之光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817f9eafed13ee935ec1efca33e71128eae90d3d","tid":917567,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"好想同佢玩到喘氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa016abc05598fa54ccc97873a9804bc0de57049","tid":917567,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"處男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講緊個浮床？"}]}